<i>Camelot!</i>

02:55:07.999 --> 02:55:09.250
<i>Camelot!</i>

02:55:09.458 --> 02:55:11.586
Yes, Camelot...

02:55:11.752 --> 02:55:13.087
...my boy.

02:55:16.090 --> 02:55:18.634
<i>Where once it never rained</i>

02:55:18.801 --> 02:55:20.761
<i>Till after sundown</i>

